    "date": "2026-04-04",
    "html": "<a href=\"https://semiengineering.com/automated-security-assertion-generation-using-llms-u-of-florida/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"block bg-slate-100/70 hover:bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">AI Infra</span>\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">今日前沿</span>\n    </div>\n    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-3\">Automated Security Assertion Generation Using LLMs (U. of Florida)</h4>\n    <p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 font-serif leading-relaxed\">利用大语言模型（LLM）进行自动化安全断言生成，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">提高了安全性和效率</span>，这是一个值得关注的技术进步。</p>\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/04/03/anthropic-is-having-a-moment-in-the-private-markets-spacex-could-spoil-the-party/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"block bg-slate-100/70 hover:bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">Agent</span>\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">今日前沿</span>\n    </div>\n    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-3\">Anthropic is having a moment in the private markets; SpaceX could spoil the party</h4>\n    <p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 font-serif leading-relaxed\">Anthropic 在私募市场上表现出色，但 <span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">SpaceX 的介入可能会改变市场格局</span>，这是一个值得关注的市场动态。</p>\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.servethehome.com/mitac-shows-servers-with-next-gen-cpus-and-solidigm-ssds-at-nvidia-gtc-2026/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"block bg-slate-100/70 hover:bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">芯片前沿</span>\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">今日前沿</span>\n    </div>\n    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-3\">MiTAC Shows Servers with Next-Gen CPUs and Solidigm SSDs at NVIDIA GTC 2026</h4>\n    <p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 font-serif leading-relaxed\">MiTAC 展示了搭载下一代 CPU 和 Solidigm SSD 的服务器，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">标志着服务器技术的重大进步</span>，值得关注的技术发展。</p>\n</a>"
  },
  {
    "date": "2026-04-09",
    "html": "<a href=\"https://semiengineering.com/pcie-8-0-enabling-the-next-generation-of-high-bandwidth-systems/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"block bg-slate-100/70 hover:bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">AI Infra</span>\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">今日前沿</span>\n    </div>\n    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-3\">PCIe 8.0: Enabling The Next Generation Of High Bandwidth Systems</h4>\n    <p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 font-serif leading-relaxed\">随着数据率的不断增加，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">维持可靠的链接需要仔细协调物理层和控制器层</span>。这对于下一代高带宽系统的发展至关重要，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">PCIe 8.0 将在其中发挥关键作用</span>。</p>\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.04937\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"block bg-slate-100/70 hover:bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">Agent</span>\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">今日前沿</span>\n    </div>\n    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-3\">Pramana: Fine-Tuning Large Language Models for Epistemic Reasoning through Navya-Nyaya</h4>\n    <p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 font-serif leading-relaxed\">大型语言模型虽然能生成流畅的文本，但在系统性推理方面存在困难，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">经常产生自信但毫无根据的说法</span>。通过 Navya-Nyaya 方法对大型语言模型进行微调，可以显著提高其在认识论推理方面的能力，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">这是人工智能研究的一个重要进展</span>。</p>\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://semiengineering.com/early-hbm4-validation-points-the-way-for-next-generation-ai-and-hpc-systems/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"block bg-slate-100/70 hover:bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl transition-colors group border border-transparent hover:border-slate-200 mb-4\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">芯片前沿</span>\n        <span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">今日前沿</span>\n    </div>\n    <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors mb-3\">Early HBM4 Validation Points The Way For Next Generation AI And HPC Systems</h4>\n    <p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 font-serif leading-relaxed\">HBM4 的早期验证标志着下一代人工智能和高性能计算系统的发展方向，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">仅仅拥有第一版芯片已经不够</span>，需要对其进行全面验证以确保其在实际应用中的可靠性和高效性，<span class=\"underline decoration-wavy decoration-blue-500 underline-offset-4 font-semibold text-slate-800\">这是芯片行业的一个重要挑战</span>。</p>\n</a>"
  }
